title: 'MacOS lies to you on opening apps'
date: '2020-01-01'
desc: 'Why is it so hard to get MacOS to open an app I want?'
tags:
  - apple
  - macos
---

MacOS: App is damaged and can't be opened.
me: `xattr -c /Applications/some.app`
MacOS: App cannot be opened because the developer cannot be verified.
me: *right-click > Open*
MacOS: App is an app downloaded from the Internet. Are you sure you want to open it?
me: *Open*
